**Analysis:**

* **Number of words:** 83
* **Number of sentences:** 6
* **Number of complex sentences (sentences with subordinate clauses):** 2
* **Number of long words (words with more than 6 letters):** 34

**LIX Calculator:**

https://www.skolverket.se/undervisning/grundskolan/grundskoleforordningen/laroplaner/aktuella-laroplaner/laroplan-for-grundskolan/bilagor-till-laroplanen/Bilaga-2-angavande-begreppet-lattlast-text

**Formula:**

```
LIX = 39 + 0.87 * (words / sentences) + 0.9 * (letters / words) + 0.6 * (complex sentences / sentences)
```

**Calculation:**

```
LIX = 39 + 0.87 * (83 / 6) + 0.9 * (400 / 83) + 0.6 * (2 / 6)
LIX = 39 + 11.97 + 4.82 + 0.2
LIX = 56
```

**Result:**

LIX = 56